        "segment": "The mapping between McCall's quality factors and ISO 9126 characteristics is not explicitly detailed in the provided context, but the ISO 9126 model focuses on user-view characteristics such as Functionality, Reliability, Usability, Efficiency, Maintainability, and Portability, which correspond broadly to McCall's factors like Correctness (Functionality), Reliability, Efficiency, Usability, Maintainability, and Portability.",
        "citations": [
